[{"time":1776015541767,"name":"city avatar","tags":"avatar","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"Photorealistic, surreal scene. A main subject sits on a stone wall in the foreground right, wearing a green traditional outfit, sunglasses, and black sandals, hand on chin. Beside them sit a brown leather suitcase and duffel bag. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. In the background, a floating island among clouds features miniature landmarks of [city], including the [landmark_1], [landmark_2], [landmark_3], and the [river] cascading off the edge as a waterfall. Golden hour lighting, blue sky, two airplanes with contrails. Cinematic depth, realistic textures.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"City name\",\"value\":\"Lahore\",\"key\":\"[city]\"},{\"label\":\"Tower landmark\",\"value\":\"Minar e Pakistan\",\"key\":\"[landmark_1]\"},{\"label\":\"Mosque landmark\",\"value\":\"Badshahi Mosque\",\"key\":\"[landmark_2]\"},{\"label\":\"Garden landmark\",\"value\":\"Shalimar Garden\",\"key\":\"[landmark_3]\"},{\"label\":\"River name\",\"value\":\"River Ravi\",\"key\":\"[river]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1776015541820.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1776015541820.png","thumbSize":"374,512","type":"image"},{"time":1776014835075,"name":"neon avatar","tags":"avatar","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A high-quality, artistic portrait of a side profile of a human subject with eyes closed, integrated with a futuristic, ethereal aesthetic. Use the attached photo as reference, keep the facial features same as much as possible. The face and neck are adorned with a luminous, glowing network of digital nodes and lines that resemble a neural network or constellation mapping. The color palette is dominated by [color1], [color2], and [color3], creating a cosmic atmosphere. The background consists of soft, bokeh-like starlight and nebulous light trails, enhancing the ethereal and tech-focused mood. The lighting is bioluminescent and cinematic, emanating from within the subject's skin and the surrounding energy field, creating a sense of deep focus and cosmic connection. Photorealistic textures with a blend of hyper-digital art style.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Deep neon blues\",\"value\":\"deep neon blues\",\"key\":\"[color1]\"},{\"label\":\"Vibrant magentas\",\"value\":\"vibrant magentas\",\"key\":\"[color2]\"},{\"label\":\"Electric purples\",\"value\":\"electric purples\",\"key\":\"[color3]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1776014835134.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1776014835134.png","thumbSize":"342,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775983431150,"name":"tech avatar","tags":"avatar, profile","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"Photorealistic 3D illustration. A realistic hand holds a smartphone. A caricature male with an oversized head, glasses, green polo, and khaki pants steps out of the screen in a 3D pop-out effect. He holds a laptop. Inside the screen are colorful paint splatters and circuit lines. Outer background is solid pale green. Text at bottom of screen reads: '[text1]'. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Bottom screen text\",\"value\":\"EMERGE - CONNECT - INNOVATE\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775983431196.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775983431196.png","thumbSize":"286,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775983352203,"name":"social avatar","tags":"avatar, profile","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A realistic 3D render of a smiling girl with long wavy purple hair, purple glasses, and a pink textured dress. She points at the camera and holds a large black ID badge. Dark blue background with floating 3D social media emojis. The badge features the text '[text1]' at the top, a circular photo placeholder in the center, '[text2]' in light blue below it, and '[text3]' in smaller text. YouTube, Instagram, and TikTok icons sit at the bottom. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Company name on badge\",\"value\":\"facebook\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Name on badge\",\"value\":\"Maria Khan\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Title on badge\",\"value\":\"Digital Creator\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775983352278.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775983352278.png","thumbSize":"342,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775936803101,"name":"text on leaf","tags":"poetry, quote","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A macro top-down view of a bright yellow autumn [object_type] resting on a clean, solid white background. The leaf has distinct natural veins and a slightly textured, organic surface. Centered on the surface of the leaf is elegant Urdu calligraphy in deep forest green ink. The text reads: '[text1] \/ [text2] \/ [text3] \/ [text4] \/ [text5]'. The lighting is soft, even, and natural, casting minimal shadows to emphasize the leaf's shape and the crispness of the written text.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Texture of the object\",\"value\":\"veined and organic\",\"key\":\"[leaf_texture]\"},{\"label\":\"Main object\",\"value\":\"leaf\",\"key\":\"[object_type]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu poetry line 1\",\"value\":\"دوست بن کر بھی نہیں ساتھ نبھانے والا\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu poetry line 2\",\"value\":\"وہی انداز ہے ظالم کا زمانے والا\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu poetry line 3\",\"value\":\"تم تکلف کو بھی اخلاص سمجھتے ہو فراز\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu poetry line 4\",\"value\":\"دوست ہوتا نہیں ہر ہاتھ ملانے والا\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Author name\",\"value\":\"احمد فراز\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775936803162.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775936803162.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775935279486,"name":"gold pendant engraved","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A close-up, high-detail macro shot of a [hand_type] holding up a polished rectangular gold pendant nec