e,"template":"A photorealistic promotional graphic design for a real estate company. The scene is dominated by a dark teal\/green mobile phone lying flat on a minimalist white surface, viewed from a high-angle isometric perspective. The phone screen displays a light gray map interface. Miniature, stylized 3D architectural models representing various properties are placed directly on the phone screen: a beige suburban house, a light gray commercial shop, a red barn\/farm complex with a greenhouse, and a multi-story modern gray commercial building. A red and green location pin icon featuring small building icons is centered on the screen. The upper visual element occupies approximately the top two-thirds of the image. Below the phone, centered in large, bold black Urdu script is the text: \"[text1]\". Immediately underneath, there is a horizontal red banner strip containing centered white English text: \"[text2]\". The bottom section of the graphic contains black contact information and branding details. Centered is the name in bold black Urdu script: \"[text3]\". Below this, in smaller Urdu script: \"[text4]\". The bottom line features contact details: a green WhatsApp icon followed by \"[text5]\", a vertical separator, a blue Facebook icon followed by \"[text6]\", a vertical separator, and a globe icon followed by \"[text7]\". Studio lighting, realistic textures, modern, clean aesthetic.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main Business Name (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"گرین سٹی رئیل اسٹیٹ\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Slogan (English)\",\"value\":\"We deal in all kind of property sell and buy\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Person's Name (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"شاکر حسین سبحانی\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Title\\\/Group Name (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"منیجنگ ڈائریکٹر گرین سٹی گروپ\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Social Media Handle\",\"value\":\"GreenCity Group\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Website\",\"value\":\"greencity.com\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775812163873.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775812163873.png","thumbSize":"384,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775811342553,"name":"social milestone","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"Dynamic 3D promotional poster with explosive lighting, sparks, and confetti. Top features spotlights illuminating 3D gold text '[text1]', above silver\/purple 3D text '[text2]' and '[text3]' with a blue verified badge. Center shows a torn purple app interface card labeled '[text4]'. Bursting through the tear is a main subject photo placeholder holding a glowing smartphone. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Floating 3D social icons surround the center amidst fiery explosions and neon beams. Bottom features a green 3D banner reading '[text5]' on a neon pedestal.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top gold text\",\"value\":\"1.5 MILLION+ APP DOWNLOADS\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main title top part\",\"value\":\"Imagitor\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main title bottom part\",\"value\":\"AI App\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"App icon\\\/UI the subject tears through\",\"value\":\"Instagram\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom ribbon text\",\"value\":\"UNLEASH YOUR CREATIVITY\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775811342626.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775811342626.png","thumbSize":"374,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775640095796,"name":"3d shop flyer","tags":"shop","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, surreal 3D promotional layout set against a smooth light sage green background with soft studio lighting and realistic shadows. In the center, a large rectangular silver metallic block serves as a base. Resting upright on the block is a giant smartwatch featuring a silver body and a large circular olive-green braided loop strap. The watch is facing down.\nInside the circular strap, on the watch face, there is a main subject sitting comfortably, wearing a light green traditional outfit and dark brown sandals, holding a silver smartphone. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Floating in the air around the giant watch are four regular-sized watches: a black smartwatch on the top-left, a gold analog watch on the mid-left, a silver metal analog watch on the top-right, and a black rugged sports watch on the mid-right. On the front face of the silver block, there is large 3D embossed metallic text reading \"[text1]\" on the top line and \"[text2]\" on the bottom line, with the main subject's feet partially resting over it. At the bottom of the image, there is 2D overlay text. On the bottom right, elegant red Urdu calligraphy reads \"[text3]\". To the left of it, smaller black Urdu text reads \"[text4]\". On the far bottom left, there is a black WhatsApp icon followed by the text \"[text5]\".","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"3D text top line\",\"value\":\"UMAIR\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"3D text bottom line\",\"value\":\"WATCHES\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Red Urdu calligraphy\",\"value\":\"عمیر واچ سنٹر\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Black Urdu text\",\"value\":\"عمدہ ، معیاری اور بہترین گھڑیوں کا مرکز\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Phone number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775640095939.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775640095939.png","thumbSize":"342,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775662347107,"name":"leather stamp","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A close-up photorealistic image capturing a luxurious, elegant detail. The background is a textured light beige or cream leather or high-quality leatherette material. Centered on this material is a circular\/oval design created using metallic gold hot foil stamping or deep embossing. The design features a thin outer gold border outlining the oval shape. Inside the oval, the primary text is stylized Arabic calligraphy, \"[text1]\", rendered prominently in rich metallic gold. Below the calligraphy, hugging the lower curve of the oval border, is text starting with a contact information symbol WhatsApp icon followed by the number \"[text2]\", also rendered in the same metallic gold foil. The lighting is soft and cinematic, highlighting the deep texture of the leather and the reflective sheen of the gold foil, creating a sense of depth and high quality. Macro lens perspective.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Arabic Calligraphy Name\",\"value\":\"صالح بن احمد\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Contact Number (including symbol)\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775662347155.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775662347155.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775662255400,"name":"stamp on leather","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A luxurious photorealistic image mockup of a circular gold foil stamped logo pressed into a dark forest green, pebbled leather surface. The logo is centered and consists of highly ornate Arabic calligraphy, \"[text1]\", rendered in tarnished metallic gold with decorative floral elements and a star accent. This central element is surrounded by a double gold ring. Below the Arabic calligraphy, wrapping in an arc along the inner edge of the gold ring, is the English text: \"[text2]\". The gold stamping is deeply debossed into the leather, catching the dramatic, warm cinematic lighting which emphasizes the texture of both the leather and the reflective quality of the gold foil. Close-up detail, sharp focus, high contrast, luxury branding aesthetic.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Central Arabic Calligraphy\",\"value\":\"جمال القرآن\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Circular English Slogan\",\"value\":\"EXPLORING THE DEEP MEANING OF LIFE THROUGH ISLAM\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775662255468.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775662255468.png","thumbSize":"512,384","type":"image"},{"time":1775652976593,"name":"toy shop flyer","tags":"flyer, shop","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A vibrant, illustrative poster with a light blue background filled with subtle, faded geometric shapes and stars. At the top, colorful triangular bunting hangs across the width. The central focus is a large, detailed toy castle with orange, blue, and green turrets. A train track circles the base with a small, colorful toy train. Sitting on top of the castle is a smiling person in a blue tunic and white pants, brown sandals. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Floating around the central figure and castle are various toys: a red and blue biplane, a cute blue robot, a small wooden pull-toy car, alphabet blocks, and a small rocket ship. A sign on the castle reads '[text1]' in red and blue letters. Below the main illustration is a white rectangular text box with rounded corners and a thin teal border. Inside the box, the main heading '[text2]' is written in a stylized, bubbly, multi-colored Urdu font with a 3D effect. Below that is smaller Urdu text '[text3]'. At the bottom center, a green WhatsApp icon is followed by the phone number '[text4]'. Scattered around the borders are small gift boxes tied with ribbons. The style is cartoonish, bright, and cheerful, similar to 3D vector illustration.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Castle Sign Text\",\"value\":\"TOY LAND\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Main Heading\",\"value\":\"سعد گفٹ سنٹر\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Address Text\",\"value\":\"مین بازار، نزدلاری اڈا، منچن آباد\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775652976662.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775652976662.png","thumbSize":"286,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775641047480,"name":"cyberpunk social","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"First-person view of a hand holding a futuristic, transparent digital glass card in a dimly lit, cyberpunk-inspired workspace. Cinematic lighting, shallow depth of field, with a softly blurred background showing a dark desk with an earbud, keyboard, and a small potted plant. The glass card features bright neon green glowing edges and holographic 3D UI elements floating around it, including a Twitter bird icon, music notes, and red hearts. On the card, the top left header features an icon with \"[text1]\" next to the text \"[text2]\" and a verified blue tick. The top right has a red glowing pill-shaped button with the text \"[text3]\". In the center is a large photo placeholder of a subject holding a smartphone, wearing glasses and a dark, intricately textured outfit. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Below the subject is a golden circular emblem adorned with metallic wings containing the cursive text \"[text4]\". Below the emblem is large, glowing white stylized text \"[text5]\". Underneath that is a subheading with crisp white text reading \"[text6]\". Below the subheading is a stats section divided into three columns: the left column has a blue user icon above \"[text7]\" and \"[text8]\", the middle column has a red heart icon above \"[text9]\" and \"[text10]\", and the right column has a blue check icon above \"[text11]\" and \"[text12]\". Below the stats is a glowing neon green outline button containing a download arrow icon and the text \"[text13]\". Below the button is elegant cursive glowing text reading \"[text14]\". At the bottom edge of the card, there is a row containing a barcode on the left, social media and app icons in the center (user profile, YouTube, Instagram, Google Play), and a QR code on the right. Below this row, running along the very bottom edge, is the fine print \"[text15]\".","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top left logo text\",\"value\":\"Ai\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Top left header name\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Live badge text\",\"value\":\"• LIVE\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Gold emblem text\",\"value\":\"Imagitor\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Main title text\",\"value\":\"AI Design\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Subtitle\\\/Categories\",\"value\":\"Creativity • Inspiration • Designs\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Followers count\",\"value\":\"1.2M\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Followers label\",\"value\":\"FOLLOWERS\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Likes count\",\"value\":\"250k\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Likes label\",\"value\":\"LIKES\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Original percentage\",\"value\":\"100%\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Original label\",\"value\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Button text\",\"value\":\"Download Now\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Thank you message\",\"value\":\"- Thank You All -\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom fine print\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI Graphic Design App\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775641047571.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775641047571.png","thumbSize":"342,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775641747640,"name":"WhatsApp social","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly detailed, 3D rendered scene featuring a large, metallic green and silver WhatsApp logo structure serving as a central seating element. The structure is thick and glossy, reflecting light softly. Sitting comfortably in the central circular cutout of the logo is a person, acting as a photo placeholder, wearing a light green traditional outfit (kurta and trousers), holding a smartphone and smiling. The person's left leg dangles over the edge, wearing black leather sandals. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Floating around the structure are various 3D chat UI elements: a white speech bubble with three dots, translucent glass panels displaying chat messages and audio waveforms, small 3D emojis (heart-eyes, smiling face, winking face), a small WhatsApp icon, and a glowing blue verified checkmark. The background is a solid, soft mint green color, providing a clean and modern aesthetic. At the base of the WhatsApp structure, large, 3D metallic silver text reads \"[text1]\" on the top line and \"[text2]\" on the bottom line. The lighting is soft and even, highlighting the metallic textures and creating a realistic, studio-quality atmosphere.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Brand Name\",\"value\":\"ImagitorAI\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"03001234567\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775641747708.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775641747708.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775641190338,"name":"youtube channel","tags":"youtube, social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic 3D scene set on a rooftop overlooking a blurred daytime cityscape. In the center stands a main subject wearing a light beige embroidered tunic, white trousers, and brown sandals, pointing directly at the camera with their right hand and holding a vlogging camera on a mini-tripod in their left hand. Behind them is a massive, highly reflective silver faceted play button logo with a glossy red center triangle, resting on a two-tiered metallic cylindrical pedestal. On the pedestal's middle tier, there is a silver plaque with the text \"[text5]\" on the left, and a glowing red neon badge with a white checkmark on the right. The base tier features large 3D silver text reading \"[text7]\". Floating around the subject are various holographic social media UI elements: on the top left, a red bubble with a heart icon and text \"[text1]\", alongside a white profile card with a small photo placeholder and the text \"[text2]\". On the bottom left, a red button with a thumbs-up icon and text \"[text3]\". On the top right, a translucent blue chart card with the text \"[text4]\", and another small profile card with a photo placeholder. On the middle right, a red button with the text \"[text6]\" and a white mouse cursor pointer. On the bottom right, a floating translucent blue bar chart. Bright natural lighting, cinematic depth of field, sharp reflections. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top left red button text\",\"value\":\"Like\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Top left profile card name\",\"value\":\"Shirley Natrigan\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom left red button text\",\"value\":\"Like\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Top right chart text\",\"value\":\"Analytics\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Middle right red button text\",\"value\":\"Subscribe\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Silver plaque text on pedestal\",\"value\":\"Subscribe\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Large 3D text on base\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775641190407.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775641190407.png","thumbSize":"374,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775627099551,"name":"Iran US news infographic","tags":"news","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"An infographic style poster with a light grey background featuring a faint geometric pattern. At the top, a large heading in Urdu reads '[text1]' and below it, an English translation reads '[text2]'. Below the heading, there are four horizontal panels stacked vertically, each with a colored outline and a distinct illustration on the left and text on the right. \n\nThe first panel has a green outline. On the left, an illustration shows a handshake between two people in dark blue suits. Above the handshake, a white dove flies between the flag of Iran on the left and the flag of the United States on the right. On the right side of the panel, a green text box contains the Urdu text '[text3]' and below it, black Urdu text reads '[text4]'.\n\nThe second panel has a blue outline. On the left, an illustration depicts the Faisal Mosque in Islamabad, Pakistan, with a long brown conference table and chairs in the foreground. On the right side of the panel, a blue text box contains the Urdu text '[text5]' and below it, black Urdu text reads '[text6]'.\n\nThe third panel has an orange outline. On the left, an illustration shows a map of the [text7] with cargo ships sailing through the blue water between yellow landmasses. The text 'Strait of Hormuz' is written on the map. On the right side of the panel, an orange text box contains the Urdu text '[text8]' and below it, black Urdu text reads '[text9]'.\n\nThe fourth panel has a red outline. On the left, an illustration shows several black oil barrels stacked next to a bar chart with a downward-pointing red arrow and the text '[text10]'. On the right side of the panel, a red text box contains the Urdu text '[text11]' and below it, black Urdu text reads '[text12]'. The overall style is clean, informative, and utilizes bright, distinct colors for each panel to separate the information visually.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Urdu Title\",\"value\":\"ایران-امریکہ تعلقات میں اہم پیش رفت\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"English Title\",\"value\":\"Iran-US Relations: Important Developments\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 1 Green Heading\",\"value\":\"ایران امریکہ سیز فائر:\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 1 Text\",\"value\":\"ایران اور امریکہ نے جنگ بندی پر اتفاق کر لیا۔\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 2 Blue Heading\",\"value\":\"مذاکرات کیلئے اسلام آباد مدعو:\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 2 Text\",\"value\":\"پاکستان نے دونوں ممالک کو مذاکرات کے لیے اسلام آباد مدعو کیا ہے۔\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Map Text\",\"value\":\"Strait of Hormuz\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 3 Orange Heading\",\"value\":\"آبنائے ہرمز سب کیلئے کھولنے کا اعلان:\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 3 Text\",\"value\":\"ایران نے آبنائے ہرمز تمام تجارتی بحری جہازوں کے لیے کھولنے کا اعلان کیا ہے۔\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Percentage Text\",\"value\":\"19%\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 4 Red Heading\",\"value\":\"تیل کی قیمتوں میں انیس فیصد کمی:\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Panel 4 Text\",\"value\":\"جنگ بندی کے بعد عالمی مارکیٹ میں خام تیل کی قیمتوں میں 19 فیصد کمی۔\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775627099678.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775627099678.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775563625218,"name":"grocery store flyer","tags":"flyer, shop","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic conceptual advertisement for a grocery delivery service. Top half: A large smartphone with a matte red case lies flat on a pristine white surface, angled slightly in perspective. The phone screen displays a light, abstract geometric map pattern in pastel tones. Arranged physically standing on the screen are miniature 3D grocery items: a red and orange box labeled \"[text1]\", a clear plastic bottle of cooking oil with a yellow cap, a small burlap sack overflowing with white flour, a dark soda bottle with a red label partially reading \"[text2]\", and a green and orange carton labeled \"[text3]\". In the center of the screen among the groceries is a red 3D map pin containing a white shopping cart icon. Soft studio lighting casts gentle shadows to the right, emphasizing the realistic textures of cardboard, plastic, glass, and burlap. Bottom half: Below the phone arrangement, placed against the clean white background, is bold black Urdu text reading \"[text4]\". Below this is a solid red rectangular banner containing the white Urdu text \"[text5]\". Further down is centered black Urdu text \"[text6]\" followed by \"[text7]\". At the very bottom, a line of text reads \"[text8]\" followed by a green WhatsApp logo icon and the phone number \"[text9]\".","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Tea box brand\",\"value\":\"TAPAL Tea\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Soda label text\",\"value\":\"Coke\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Juice box text\",\"value\":\"Juice\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Main Urdu heading\",\"value\":\"گروسری کی تمام اشیا دستیاب ہیں\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Red banner Urdu text\",\"value\":\"ہوم ڈیلیوری دستیاب ہے\"},{\"key\":\"[text6]\",\"label\":\"Store name in Urdu\",\"value\":\"شکیل کیش اینڈ کیری\"},{\"key\":\"[text7]\",\"label\":\"Address in Urdu\",\"value\":\"ڈیفنس روڈ، نزد فلائی اوور، ملتان\"},{\"key\":\"[text8]\",\"label\":\"Contact prompt text\",\"value\":\"For order contact us at\"},{\"key\":\"[text9]\",\"label\":\"Phone number\",\"value\":\"0300 1234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775563625276.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775563625276.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775561776811,"name":"calligraphy text logo","tags":"logo","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic close-up of elegant metallic gold calligraphy on thick, textured white paper. The design forms a balanced, circular composition. In the center, there is ornate Arabic calligraphy reading \"[text1]\" with intricate flourishes, sweeping curves, and decorative diacritics. The style is a freehand, fluid monogram blending the exaggerated, graceful curves of Diwani script with the strong, structured elegance of Thuluth script. The typography features extremely flowing, swirly, fluid-like golden strokes with exaggerated, sweeping tails and elegant curves. The ink is rich, smooth, and dynamic, appearing like liquid flowing gracefully across the canvas. Curving along the bottom edge of the circular design is the English text \"[text2]\" written in a graceful, sweeping cursive script with long, elegant tails. Soft, natural directional lighting catches the metallic sheen of the gold ink, highlighting its highly reflective, embossed surface against the matte, subtly shadowed grain of the premium white watercolor paper.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Arabic calligraphy text\",\"value\":\"مكتبة رحمانية\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"English cursive text\",\"value\":\"Excellence in Publishing\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775561776874.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775561776874.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775544797861,"name":"shop on map","tags":"business, flyer","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A vertical promotional flyer divided into two distinct sections: at two third top 3D isometric illustration and at the one third bottom an ornate 2D graphic banner. Top Section: A photorealistic 3D isometric rendering of a modern, miniature white two-story shop building set on a light gray city street map background with light blue road lines. The building has dark glass windows, a glass storefront door, silver roof railings, and air conditioning units on the side wall. A prominent rooftop billboard displays the text \"[text1]\". Above the storefront entrance, another sign reads \"[text2]\". Parked outside the shop are miniature vehicles: a beige and brown auto-rickshaw on the left, and a white scooter alongside a black motorcycle in the center. Placed on the map around the building as oversized 3D objects are three watches: a [watch1] on the left, a [watch2] on the front right, and a [watch3] on the back right. The lighting is soft, natural, and creates realistic cast shadows, giving a miniature diorama effect. Bottom Section: An elegant flat graphic banner featuring intricate traditional Islamic geometric and floral border patterns in rich navy blue, gold, and dark red. The ornate borders frame a white scalloped central area. Inside this white space, large, elegant dark red Urdu typography reads \"[text3]\". Below it, black Urdu text says \"[text4]\" and \"[text5]\". At the very bottom, a green WhatsApp icon sits next to the text \"[text6]\", and a blue Facebook icon sits next to the text \"[text7]\".","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Rooftop billboard text\",\"value\":\"عمیر واچ سٹور\",\"key\":\"[t