tered near the bottom, elegant black text reads \"[text14]\". At the very bottom, a dark green solid footer banner matching the top contains crisp white text \"[text15]\".","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top right header text\",\"value\":\"سرکاری سکول\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Top left header text\",\"value\":\"معیاری سکول\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main title text Urdu\",\"value\":\"داخلہ مہم\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Main title text English\",\"value\":\"Admission Campaign\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Badge text\",\"value\":\"داخلہ جاری ہے\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Main school name calligraphy\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز پرائمری سکول علی پور\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"School gate signboard text\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز پرائمری سکول علی پور\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 1\",\"value\":\"مفت داخلہ\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 2\",\"value\":\"مفت کتابیں\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 3\",\"value\":\"اعلیٰ کوالیفائیڈ اسٹاف\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 4\",\"value\":\"کھلے کشادہ کلاس رومز\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 5\",\"value\":\"پلے گراؤنڈز\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"List item 6\",\"value\":\"بہترین رزلٹس\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom tagline text\",\"value\":\"ایک بہترین ادارہ، ایک روشن مستقبل\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer school name text\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز پرائمری سکول علی پور\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775247185770.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775247185770.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775246413247,"name":"school admissions","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic educational promotional flyer. The background is a softly blurred, bright classroom interior featuring empty wooden desks and natural light coming from windows, creating a shallow depth of field. On the right side, a main subject photo placeholder s