, '[text15]', and '[text16]'.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top header line 1\",\"value\":\"Bright Future\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Top header line 2\",\"value\":\"Public School\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Alphabet poster text\",\"value\":\"ABCD EFGHI IJKLM NNOOP QRSTU V\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Middle left text 1\",\"value\":\"Ready\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Middle left text 2\",\"value\":\"for\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Middle left text 3\",\"value\":\"Future\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Book title\",\"value\":\"EXPLORING SCIENCE\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Book subtitle\",\"value\":\"Grade 3\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Blazer badge text\",\"value\":\"BFPS\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom left text 1\",\"value\":\"ADMISSION\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom left text 2\",\"value\":\"OPEN\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer banner text 1\",\"value\":\"Introducing Digital Curriculum for Future Ready Studies\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer school name\",\"value\":\"Bright Future Public School\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer address\",\"value\":\"Main Shami Road, Lahore\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer phone number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer website\",\"value\":\"www.brightfuture.edu.pk\",\"key\":\"[text16]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775229504321.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775229504321.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775229396287,"name":"school admissions digital","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A brightly lit, modern classroom scene with soft pink walls. In the upper right corner, large white sans-serif text reads '[text1]' To the left, a student in a burgundy and navy blue school uniform sits at a light wooden desk, reading a blue book titled '[text2]'. Next to the student sits a small, friendly white and blue robot, also looking at the book. On the wall behind them, there is a '[text3]', a poster of a forest, and a corkboard. To the right of the student and robot, 3D bubble letters with an orange gradient and blue outline read '[text4]'. Below this, large red 3D bubble letters read '[text5]'. In the bottom left corner, a stack of colorful textbooks rests next to a tablet displaying a bright blue screen with the text '[text6]'. The spine of the blue book in the stack reads '[text7]', the red spine reads '[text8]', the green spine reads '[text9]', and the brown spine reads '[text10]'. In the bottom center, black sans-serif text reads '[text11]'. In the bottom right corner, black sans-serif text reads '[text12]', followed by '[text13]', '[text14]', and '[text15]'. The overall style is a clean, bright, and engaging educational advertisement.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top right headline\",\"value\":\"Bright Future Public School.\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Book title\",\"value\":\"MY WORLD EXPLORERS\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Wall chart title\",\"value\":\"Multiplication Chart\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Middle right bubble text\",\"value\":\"Ready for future\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Lower right bubble text\",\"value\":\"Admission Open\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Tablet screen text\",\"value\":\"DIGITAL LEARNING\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Blue book spine\",\"value\":\"SCIENCE\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Red book spine\",\"value\":\"MATH\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Green book spine\",\"value\":\"MATH\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Brown book spine\",\"value\":\"STORIES\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom center text\",\"value\":\"Introducing Digital Curriculum for Future Ready Studies\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom right school name\",\"value\":\"Bright Future Public School\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Address line 1\",\"value\":\"Main Shami Road, Lahore\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone number\",\"valu