d \"[text22]\". A block of descriptive text is placed centrally near the bottom: \"[text23] [text24]\". The contact number \"[text25]\" is large, black, and centered below the descriptive text. The bottom edge features a horizontal cream\/gold band containing the address text: \"[text26]\". The lighting is dramatic and cinematic, highlighting the 3D structure and metallic gold accents.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Descriptor 1 (Top Right)\",\"value\":\"منفرد انداز میں\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title\",\"value\":\"درس نظامی\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Descriptor 2 (Top Left)\",\"value\":\"داخلے جاری ہیں\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Logo Acronym\",\"value\":\"D.U.I\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Logo Name\",\"value\":\"دار العلم\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (1st Course)\",\"value\":\"1 سال\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (1st Course)\",\"value\":\"فہم اللسان کورس\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Start Date\",\"value\":\"داخلوں کا آغاز : 01 مئی 2025\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Time\",\"value\":\"وقت: صبح 9 تا 12 بجے\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (2nd Course)\",\"value\":\"2 سال\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (2nd Course)\",\"value\":\"فہم قرآن کورس\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (3rd Course)\",\"value\":\"2 سال\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (3rd Course)\",\"value\":\"فہم فقہ کورس\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (4th Course)\",\"value\":\"2 سال\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (4th Course)\",\"value\":\"فہم حدیث کورس\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (5th Course)\",\"value\":\"1 سال\",\"key\":\"[text16]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (5th Course)\",\"value\":\"دوره حدیث\",\"key\":\"[text17]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Duration (6th Course)\",\"value\":\"1 سال\",\"key\":\"[text18]\"},{\"label\":\"Course Name (6th Course)\",\"value\":\"دوره قرآن\",\"key\":\"[text19]\"},{\"label\":\"Supervision Label\",\"value\":\"زیر نگرانی\",\"key\":\"[text20]\"},{\"label\":\"Supervisor Name\",\"value\":\"علامہ فرحان علوی صاحب\",\"key\":\"[text21]\"},{\"label\":\"Supervisor Title\\\/Institute\",\"value\":\"پرنسپل دار العلم انسٹیٹیوٹ\",\"key\":\"[text22]\"},{\"label\":\"Detail Text Part 1\",\"value\":\"فہم فقہ، دورہ حدیث اور دورہ قرآن کے علاوہ تمام کورسز میں س\",\"key\":\"[text23]\"},{\"label\":\"Detail Text Part 2\",\"value\":\"معاملات کے لیے اکیڈمی یا دیئے گئے نمبر پر جلد از جلد رابطہ فرمائیں۔\",\"key\":\"[text24]\"},{\"label\":\"Contact Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text25]\"},{\"label\":\"Address\\\/Location\",\"value\":\"دار العلم انسٹیٹیوٹ : متصل جامع مسجد فاروق، مین شاہراہ، مدینتہ العلم\",\"key\":\"[text26]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775219846951.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775219846951.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775219419998,"name":"Islamic madrassa","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A professional educational flyer design with a clean, modern aesthetic. The background is a teal color with a subtle, intricate repeating geometric pattern. At the top right is a circular logo featuring a book icon and Arabic text. The top headline reads '[text1]' in large, elegant Urdu calligraphy. Below this is a highlighted box with text '[text2]' and '[text3]'. The middle section contains a grid of rounded rectangular tiles in teal and orange featuring text: '[text4]', '[text5]', '[text6]', '[text7]', '[text8]', '[text9]', '[text10]', '[text11]'. Towards the bottom, there is an ornate gold-bordered frame containing text: '[text12]', '[text13]'. The very bottom has a phone number '[text14]' and text '[text15]'. The overall style is organized, academic, and professional, using high-contrast typography and flat graphic elements.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"School Name\",\"value\":\"الہدیٰ ماڈل سکول، لاہور\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Admission Status\",\"value\":\"طلباء وطالبات کیلئے داخلہ جاری ہے\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Grade Range\",\"value\":\"پلے گروپ تا جماعت ہشتم\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Feature 1\",\"value\":\"انتہائی مناسب فیس\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Feature 2\",\"value\":\"قابل اور محنتی اسٹاف\"},{\"key\":\"[text6]\",\"label\":\"Feature 3\",\"value\":\"دنیاوی تعلیم کے ساتھ ساتھ  دینی تعلیم و تربیت\"},{\"key\":\"[text7]\",\"label\":\"Feature 4\",\"value\":\"اعلیٰ معیار تعلیم\"},{\"key\":\"[text8]\",\"label\":\"Feature 5\",\"value\":\"سیکیورٹی کا اعلیٰ انتظام\"},{\"key\":\"[text9]\",\"label\":\"Feature 6\",\"value\":\"بچوں کے والدین کے ساتھ ماہانہ میٹنگ\"},{\"key\":\"[text10]\",\"label\":\"Feature 7\",\"value\":\"صاف ستھرا ماحول\"},{\"key\":\"[text11]\",\"label\":\"Feature 8\",\"value\":\"کشادہ ہوادار کمرے\"},{\"key\":\"[text12]\",\"label\":\"Result Headline\",\"value\":\"ہر سال پنجم اور ہشتم بورڈ کا رزلٹ 100%\"},{\"key\":\"[text13]\",\"label\":\"Achievement Details\",\"value\":\"سال 2028ء میں ہشتم بورڈ کے امتحان میں طالب علم محمد بن یوسف نے بہترین نمبروں کے ذریعے اسکالر شپ حاصل کی۔\"},{\"key\":\"[text14]\",\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"},{\"key\":\"[text15]\",\"label\":\"Address\\\/Footer\",\"value\":\"زیر نگرانی انتظامی کمیٹی الہدیٰ تعلیمی کمپلیکس، گلبرگ، لاہور\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775219420086.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775219420086.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775219211474,"name":"madrassa quran hifz","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A high-resolution, full-page advertisement poster design for an Islamic educational academy, rendered in a professional graphic design style with photorealistic texture emphasis. The background is light beige with a subtle, repeating Islamic geometric pattern. The top right features large, bold, raised red Arabic calligraphy with a subtle 3D effect: \"[text1]\". Small white Plumeria flowers are scattered around this text. On the top left is a vertical, shield-shaped logo emblem rendered in gold and deep green, containing the white text: \"ACADEMY OF QURANIC EDUCATION Est. 2024\". Below the headline is a decorative horizontal banner in deep green with gold ornate borders containing the white text: \"[text8]\". The poster is divided into two main vertical sections. The right section features a gold\/brown scroll element containing the text: \"[text2]\", \"[text3]\", \"[text4]\", \"[text5]\", and \"[text6]\". Below this, a yellow panel is titled \"شرائط داخلہ\" (black text). The conditions listed in black text, each preceded by a relevant icon (camera, ID card, student cap, globe\/web icon) are: \"[text10]\", \"[text11]\", \"[text12]\", \"[text13]\", \"[text14]\", and \"[text15]\". At the bottom of the right section, a small purple banner contains the section title \"[text16]\" and the date \"[text17]\". The main left panel is a stack of color-coded horizontal rectangles representing features. A vertical deep green label banner runs down the left side with the white text \"خصوصیات\". The features listed in black text on alternating colored boxes (light blue, pink, light green, light orange, light yellow, pale green, light grey) are: \"[text19]\", \"[text20]\", \"[text21]\", \"[text22]\", \"[text23]\", \"[text24]\", and \"[text25]\". The entire design is anchored by a prominent, full-width deep green footer banner. It contains address information in large yellow text: \"[text26]\". Below that, the call to action \"[text27]\" in yellow, and the large white phone number: \"[text28]\".","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Main Headline Text (Arabic Calligraphy)\",\"value\":\"حفظ القرآن میں\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Supervision Text 1\",\"value\":\"زیر نگرانی\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Supervision Text 2\",\"value\":\"فضیلة الشیخ\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Supervision Text 3\",\"value\":\"حفظه الله\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Main Name\",\"value\":\"قاری محمد یوسف\"},{\"key\":\"[text6]\",\"label\":\"Name Descriptor\",\"value\":\"عالم دین، استاد قرآءت\"},{\"key\":\"[text7]\",\"label\":\"Logo Text\",\"value\":\"ACADEMY OF\\nQURANIC\\nEDUCATION\\nEst. 2024\"},{\"key\":\"[text8]\",\"label\":\"Admission Status Banner Text\",\"value\":\"محدود نشستوں پر داخلے جاری ہیں\"},{\"key\":\"[text9]\",\"label\":\"Admission Conditions Title\",\"value\":\"شرائط داخله\"},{\"key\":\"[text10]\",\"label\":\"Condition 1 (Photos)\",\"value\":\"دو عدد تصاویر\"},{\"key\":\"[text11]\",\"label\":\"Condition 2 (ID Card)\",\"value\":\"نقل شناختی کارڈ سرپرست\"},{\"key\":\"[text12]\",\"label\":\"Condition 3 (Education requirement)\",\"value\":\"طالبعلم پرائمری پاس ہو\"},{\"key\":\"[text13]\",\"label\":\"Condition 4 (Guardian requirement)\",\"value\":\"سرپرست کا ساتھ آنا ضروری ہے\"},{\"key\":\"[text14]\",\"label\":\"Condition 5 (School certificate)\",\"value\":\"سابقہ اسکول \\\/ مدرسہ چھوڑنے کا سر ٹیفکیٹ\"},{\"key\":\"[text15]\",\"label\":\"Condition 6 (Birth proof)\",\"value\":\"تاریخ پیدائش کا سرکاری ثبوت (ب فارم)\"},{\"key\":\"[text16]\",\"label\":\"Class Start Title\",\"value\":\"کلاسوں کا آغاز\"},{\"key\":\"[text17]\",\"label\":\"Class Start Date\",\"value\":\"یکم اکتوبر 2026\"},{\"key\":\"[text18]\",\"label\":\"Features Label (Vertical)\",\"value\":\"خصوصيات\"},{\"key\":\"[text19]\",\"label\":\"Feature 1 (Teachers)\",\"value\":\"کلاس کے لیے قابل اور محنتی اساتذہ کی خدمات\"},{\"key\":\"[text20]\",\"label\":\"Feature 2 (Supplication\\\/Prayers)\",\"value\":\"بچوں کی تربیت اور ادعیہ مسنونہ کا اہتمام\"},{\"key\":\"[text21]\",\"label\":\"Feature 3 (Evaluation)\",\"value\":\"یومیہ اور ماہانہ جائزہ (رپورٹ سسٹم)\"},{\"key\":\"[text22]\",\"label\":\"Feature 4 (Tajweed Rules)\",\"value\":\"قواعد تجوید پر خصوصی توجہ\"},{\"key\":\"[text23]\",\"label\":\"Feature 5 (Arabic Dialects)\",\"value\":\"عربی لہجات کی مشق\"},{\"key\":\"[text24]\",\"label\":\"Feature 6 (Corporal Punishment)\",\"value\":\"جسمانی سزا کا مکمل خاتمہ\"},{\"key\":\"[text25]\",\"label\":\"Feature 7 (Environment)\",\"value\":\"مشفقانہ تربیتی ماحول\"},{\"key\":\"[text26]\",\"label\":\"Address Text\",\"value\":\"جامع مسجد رحمانیه شاہراہ تعلیم (نزد الفلاح سکوائر) تعلیم آباد، نیوسٹی\"},{\"key\":\"[text27]\",\"label\":\"Call to Action\",\"value\":\"داخلے کے لیے ابھی رابطہ کریں! رابطہ:\"},{\"key\":\"[text28]\",\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775219211576.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775219211576.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775219083694,"name":"hifz quran madrassa","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A vertical informational flyer designed in a traditional Islamic graphic style. The background is a textured cream or tan parchment simulating paper. The overall color palette features deep teal blue, olive green, and gold accents. The top section is dominated by a deep teal curved shape containing large, flowing white Arabic calligraphy reading '[text1]'. A smaller brown\/tan curved overlay is positioned on the top left, hosting a logo depicting an open book under a dome\/minaret silhouette, followed by the text '[text8]', '[text9]', and '[text10]'. A thick, tilted olive-green banner crosses the upper center, displaying the prominent white Arabic text '[text6]', flanked by small gold floral asterisks. Above this banner, in smaller black text, are '[text4]' and '[text5]'. Below the banner, in small black text, is '[text7]'. On the top right, below the teal area, the text '[text2]' is placed, followed by the large, stylized dark blue name text '[text3]'. The main central body is split into two sections: The left section lists features under the vertical label '[text11]', detailing points like '[text12]', '[text13]', '[text14]', '[text15]', '[text16]', '[text17]', and '[text18]', marked by small gold asterisks. The right section, titled '[text19]', is contained within an arched decorative frame (Mihrab style) featuring geometric Islamic patterns, listing requirements: '[text20]', '[text21]', '[text22]', '[text23]', '[text24]', and '[text25]', marked by brown dots. The bottom footer is a solid deep teal blue strip. The center of the footer contains the blue text '[text26]' followed by the address '[text27]'. The phone number '[text28]' is prominently displayed in large white font below the address. Use photorealistic rendering of high-quality printed paper and professional calligraphy.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main title text (Top calligraphy)\",\"value\":\"حفظ القرآن میں\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Supervision label\",\"value\":\"زیر نگرانی\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Name of supervisor\",\"value\":\"حافظ مولانا محمد احسان\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Limited seats part 1\",\"value\":\"محدود\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Limited seats part 2\",\"value\":\"نشستوں پر\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission status banner text\",\"value\":\"داخلے جاری ہیں\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Start date\",\"value\":\"یکم جولائی 2026 سے\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"English institute name part 1\",\"value\":\"AL-HIKMAH\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"English institute name part 2\",\"value\":\"EDUCATIONAL CENTER\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu institute name\",\"value\":\"الکمہ ایجوکیشنل سنٹر\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Features section title\",\"value\":\"خصوصیات:\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 1 (Teachers)\",\"value\":\"کلاس کے لیے قابل اور محنتی اساتذہ کی خدمات\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 2 (Training)\",\"value\":\"بچوں کی تربیت اور ادعیہ مسنونہ کا اہتمام\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 3 (Assessment)\",\"value\":\"یومیہ اور ماہانہ جائزہ (رپورٹ سسٹم)\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 4 (Tajweed)\",\"value\":\"قواعد تجوید پر خصوصی توجہ\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 5 (Arabic accent practice)\",\"value\":\"عربی لہجات کی مشق\",\"key\":\"[text16]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 6 (No corporal punishment)\",\"value\":\"جسمانی سزا کا مکمل خاتمہ\",\"key\":\"[text17]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature point 7 (Environment)\",\"value\":\"شفاف تربیتی ماحول\",\"key\":\"[text18]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission requirements section title\",\"value\":\"شرائط داخلہ\",\"key\":\"[text19]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 1 (Photos)\",\"value\":\"دو عدد تصاویر\",\"key\":\"[text20]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 2 (Guardian ID)\",\"value\":\"نقل شناختی کارڈ سر پرست\",\"key\":\"[text21]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 3 (Education level)\",\"value\":\"طالب علم پرائمری پاس ہو\",\"key\":\"[text22]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 4 (Guardian presence)\",\"value\":\"سرپرست کے ساتھ آنا ضروری ہے\",\"key\":\"[text23]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 5 (Leaving Certificate)\",\"value\":\"سابقہ اسکول \\\/ مدرسہ چھوڑنے کا سرٹیفکیٹ\",\"key\":\"[text24]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement point 6 (Birth proof)\",\"value\":\"تاریخ پیدائش کا سرکاری ثبوت (ب فارم)\",\"key\":\"[text25]\"},{\"label\":\"Institution\\\/Masjid name (Footer)\",\"value\":\"جامع مسجد التقویٰ\",\"key\":\"[text26]\"},{\"label\":\"Address details (Footer)\",\"value\":\"فیض عام روڈ (نزد شاہین مارکیٹ) ماڈل ٹاؤن ، اسلام آباد\",\"key\":\"[text27]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone number (Footer)\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text28]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775219083812.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775219083812.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775213447455,"name":"madrassa admission","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A high-resolution, photorealistic image of a vibrant, professionally designed Islamic school admission flyer (poster style) set against a light sky-blue background featuring faint, subtle white silhouettes of mosque domes and minarets. The design utilizes bright, even cinematic lighting. At the very top, two white, cloud-shaped text boxes are placed symmetrically. The left cloud contains the text: \"[text1] [text2]\". The right cloud contains the text: \"[text4] [text5]\". The main central 