s same as much as possible. Below the photo, the name '[text3]' is written in bold gold font, followed by '[text4]' and '[text5]'. At the bottom, a rectangular border encloses details with icons: '[text6]', '[text7]', and '[text8]'. The overall style is respectful, solemn, and high-quality digital print.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Arabic funeral verse\",\"value\":\"إِنَّا لِلَّٰهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Funeral prayer title\",\"value\":\"نمازِ جنازہ\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Name of the deceased\",\"value\":\"ناصرالدین صاحب\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Profession label\",\"value\":\"حاجی کریانہ سٹور\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Condolence message\",\"value\":\"جوکہ قضائے الہی سے وفات پاگئے تھے۔\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Day of the week\",\"value\":\"دن: بروز جمعرات\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Time of funeral\",\"value\":\"وقت: دوپہر 2:00 بجے\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Location of funeral\",\"value\":\"مقام: مدرسہ انوارِ اسلام\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775116697176.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775116697176.png","thumbSize":"512,383","type":"image"},{"time":1775116650915,"name":"اعلان وفات obituary","tags":"wafaat","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A professional Islamic-style funeral announcement poster. The background is a dark forest green with a subtle, glowing silhouette of mosque minarets and domes in the distance. Centered at the top is a vertical rectangular photo placeholder framed with an ornate golden archway design featuring intricate filigree patterns. Below the photo is the text '[text1]' in bold white calligraphy, followed by '[text2]' in smaller white text. Below that, a green decorative badge contains the text '[text3]'. At the bottom, a rectangular container with a lighter green border houses three lines of text with icons: a calendar icon followed by '[text4]', a clock icon followed by '[text5]', and a mosque icon followed by '[te