gold trim. On this banner, the title is written in large, white-gold Urdu script: [text5]. The bottom section contains event details laid out horizontally within a long, ornate, dark brown\/gold bordered panel. This panel is divided into three sections, each with a small gold icon (a calendar\/date icon, a clock icon, and a mosque\/building icon). The details, separated by vertical dividers, read: Left section: [text6], Center section: [text7], Right section: [text8]. The overall aesthetic is high contrast, formal, and traditional, with realistic materials and dramatic lighting.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top religious calligraphy\",\"value\":\"انا لله وانا اليه راجعون\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main name\",\"value\":\"محمد جمیل وارث صاحب\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Designation\\\/Affiliation in parentheses\",\"value\":\"(حارث ہوٹل والے)\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Condolence statement\",\"value\":\"جو کہ قضائے الہی سے وفات پاگئے تھے۔\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Event type title\",\"value\":\"نماز جنازه\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Event day detail\",\"value\":\"دن: بروز جمعرات\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Event time detail\",\"value\":\"وقت: دو پہر 2:00 بجے\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Event location detail\",\"value\":\"مقام : مدرسہ انوار اسلام\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775116593418.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775116593418.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775113700981,"name":"green name style","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, luxurious 3D render of a decorative square plaque. The central background is deep emerald green velvet or silk fabric featuring a subtle damask pattern. This field is surrounded by an elaborate, ornate, gold metallic frame with intricate arabesque detailing, giving it a baroque look. Dominating the center are large, three-dimensional characters in highly polished silver chrome calligraphy reading: '[text1]'. Positioned above the text is a smaller, 3D golden crescent moon and five-pointed star symbol. The scene is lit with dramatic, cinematic studio lighting, emphasizing the metallic textures, reflections, and deep shadows against the rich green background.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Central Calligraphy Text\",\"value\":\"سُہیل اَحمد رَضا\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775113701046.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775113701046.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775112704093,"name":"name calligraphy","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A luxurious, photorealistic 3D render of a formal square presentation image. The background is a [text4] or embossed leather with subtle damask patterns, creating a dark vignette around the edges. A highly ornate, detailed gold frame with intricate traditional Islamic arabesque patterns surrounds the central area. The frame is thick, reflective, and appears deeply embossed. Centered prominently is large, highly polished 3D Arabic calligraphy in [text2] material, reading: [text1]. The calligraphy style is [text3], rendered with high relief and casting subtle shadows. Above the calligraphy, centered near the top edge, is a small, polished gold crescent moon and star symbol. Cinematic, dramatic studio lighting emphasizes the reflective surfaces of the gold, creating bright specular highlights and deep shadows, giving the overall image a feeling of richness and depth.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Name\\\/Calligraphy\",\"value\":\"محمد جنید بغدادی\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Text Color\\\/Material\",\"value\":\"Brilliant Gold Metallic\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Text Style\",\"value\":\"Elegant 3D Kufic\\\/Thuluth\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Background Color\\\/Texture\",\"value\":\"Deep Royal Blue Velvet\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1775112704180.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1775112704180.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775093940944,"name":