ogo. The character has a positive expression and is giving a thumbs-up gesture. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Behind the character is a large, rectangular screen displaying a glowing Facebook profile page interface. The screen has a vibrant blue outline. On the profile page banner area, there is a circular photo placeholder of the same character. Above the cover photo area, the word \"[text1]\" appears in the top left corner of the screen UI. The profile name section in the banner shows \"[text2]\" followed by \"[text3]\". Below the banner, the main profile information is visible: \"[text4]\", and underneath that, \"[text5]\". Below the name, there are navigation tabs: \"[text6]\", \"[text7]\", \"[text8]\", and \"[text9]\". A section header reads \"[text10]\" lower down. Floating around the scene are various 3D design-related icons: a camera icon, a palette icon, and two code bracket icons (< \/ >). The environment features a wooden floor, a dark rug, and background elements like a small wooden shelf with a camera, and a partial view of a desk setup to the right. Cinematic lighting with strong blue rim lights and soft shadows.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Facebook UI header text\",\"value\":\"facebook\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Name in banner area\",\"value\":\"Ahmed Jehanzeb\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Title in banner area\",\"value\":\"AI Graphic Designer\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Main profile name\",\"value\":\"Ahmed Jehanzeb\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Main profile title\",\"value\":\"AI Graphic Designer\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 1\",\"value\":\"Home\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 2\",\"value\":\"About\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 3\",\"value\":\"Previous\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 4\",\"value\":\"More\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Section header\",\"value\":\"About\",\"k