 is intricate gold foil framing over a cream textured background, with dark teal, patterned corner elements adorned with hanging gold geometric ornaments. The design style is photorealistic with vector graphic overlays (image style). The text is layered prominently in black and deep blue Arabic\/Urdu script, styled formally.\n\nTop center, aligned small: \"[text1]\".\nBelow that, in large deep blue script, centered: \"[text2]\".\nBelow that, centered: \"[text3]\".\nBelow that, in very large, bold deep blue script: \"[text4]\".\n\nA wide, curved golden banner sits below, containing the text: \"[text5]\".\nBelow this, a second, darker teal\/green gradient banner, highly decorative with gold trim, contains the enrollment period text: \"[text6]\".\n\nIn the middle section, spanning the width above the mosque photo, are two adjacent sections:\nLeft section (on a gold banner): Title \"[text7]\". Below the title, three bullet points in black text, centered: \"[text8]\", \"[text9]\", and \"[text10]\".\nRight section (on a gold banner): Title \"[text11]\". Below the title, five bullet points in black text, left-aligned: \"[text12]\", \"[text13]\", \"[text14]\", \"[text15]\", and \"[text16]\".\n\nBelow the list sections, centered above the base of the mosque: Title \"[text17]\".\nBelow this title, two bullet points in black text: \"[text18]\" and \"[text19]\".\n\nAt the very bottom, a gold-trimmed teal banner\/footer element holds the contact information.\nAbove the footer, small text: \"[text20]\".\nCentered in the footer, large, bold contact numbers: \"[text21]\".\n\nPhotorealistic style, cinematic lighting, high detail, traditional Urdu\/Arabic calligraphy fonts.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Bismillah calligraphy (Top blessing)\",\"value\":\"بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Institute Name (Main Title)\",\"value\":\"مدرسه اشاعت التوحید\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Location\\\/Address\",\"value\":\"تحصیل و ضلع سیالکوٹ\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"