intricate gold and burgundy decorative borders. Centered at the top, an elaborate gold-trimmed, ornamental burgundy cartouche holds the primary title text \"[text1]\" in large white serif font, followed by \"[text2]\" in large white bold font below it. The upper background is light cream with subtle, faint line art doodles of academic objects. Below the main banner, the large Urdu calligraphy text \"[text3]\" is centrally placed in white. Directly beneath this, a smaller line of Urdu text \"[text4]\" is placed above a dark blue\/teal horizontal school signboard. The sign features \"[text5]\" in white capital letters, with \"[text6]\" centered in a smaller white font beneath it, flanked by two circular institutional logos. The main visual composition features a highly detailed illustration of a school entrance with high reddish-brown brick walls and a tall black wrought-iron gate, illuminated by bright daylight. Three figures in matching blue and white school uniforms (shalwar kameez style) are walking directly toward the viewer, holding books, emerging from the gate area. Centered above the figures and overlaid on the illustration, a dark burgundy ribbon banner holds the white invitation text: \"[text7]\". Centered near the bottom, an ornate, gold-rimmed horizontal oval badge contains the final date text: \"[text8]\" in bold black font. Highly detailed digital painting style, photorealistic textures, rich color palette.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 1\",\"value\":\"Annual Result\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 2 (Year)\",\"value\":\"2026\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Urdu School Name (Large)\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز ہائی سکول فتح پور\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Secondary Urdu School Name (Small)\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز بھائی سکول فخ پور\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"English School Name Part 1\",\"value\":\"GOVERNMENT GIRLS HIGH SCHOOL FATEHĪ\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"English School Name Part 2 