hotorealistic, highly detailed image of a thick, transparent acrylic or glass display plaque standing upright on a glossy, polished white marble desk surface. The plaque features a semi-transparent, vertically oriented portrait photo placeholder of a professional subject in a dark blue suit embedded on the left side. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. The right side of the plaque displays glowing cyan text in a clean, modern sans-serif font. The surface below shows a clear reflection of the plaque, the photo, and the glowing text. Text placement: The first line of text, \"[text1]\", is top-right, followed by the larger text \"[text2]\" directly below it. The job title \"[text3]\" is smaller and centered below the name. Further down, there is a glowing WhatsApp icon followed by the contact information. The line \"[text4]\" precedes the number \"[text5]\". The entire scene is set in a blurred, modern, cool-toned corporate office environment with soft ambient lighting creating a deep bokeh effect. The overall lighting is cinematic and focused on the glowing elements of the glass.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"First name\",\"value\":\"Asif\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Last name\",\"value\":\"Mehmood\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Job title\",\"value\":\"(AI Graphic Designer)\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Contact label prefix\",\"value\":\"WhatsApp:\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Phone number suffix\",\"value\":\"03001234567\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1774849430069.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1774849430069.png","thumbSize":"385,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774793541295,"name":"desk name","tags":"social, business","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A realistic, high-quality wooden desk plaque featuring a portrait relief sculpture of a person on the left side. The plaque is made of dark polished walnut wood with a prominent grain texture. On the right side, there is pro