es) are spilling out of the hole, scattering onto the wet, reflective pavement below.\nText Placement:\nTop header features a search bar containing \"[text3]\" and an avatar placeholder next to \"[text1]\". The top right corner includes the icon \"[text32]\".\nThe left navigation bar lists: \"[text8]\" (with an avatar placeholder), \"[text9]\", \"[text10]\", \"[text11]\", \"[text12]\", \"[text13]\", \"[text14]\", \"[text15]\", \"[text16]\", \"[text17]\", \"[text18]\", and \"[text19]\". The main post section includes a placeholder avatar and \"[text4]\" followed by \"[text5]\". The main text is centered over the subject: \"[text6] [text7]\".\nBelow the subject, the post footer shows reaction icons, \"[text20]\", \"[text21]\", \"Like\", \"[text23]\", and a comment input box stating \"[text24]\" (with an avatar placeholder).\nA right sidebar section is partially visible, featuring \"[text25]\", \"[text26]\" (with an avatar placeholder), \"[text27]\", \"[text28]\" (with an avatar placeholder), \"[text29]\", \"[text30]\", and \"[text31]\".\nThe Facebook logo is prominently displayed on the top left, labeled \"[text2]\". An overhead streetlamp provides harsh top-down illumination on the upper left.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Header profile name\",\"value\":\"Shahid Hussain\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Facebook logo text\",\"value\":\"facebook\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Search bar text\",\"value\":\"Search\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Post title (small)\",\"value\":\"Tech With Shahid Hussain:\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Post time stamp\",\"value\":\"13 mins\"},{\"key\":\"[text6]\",\"label\":\"Post title (large)\",\"value\":\"Tech With Shahid Hussain:\"},{\"key\":\"[text7]\",\"label\":\"Main body text\",\"value\":\"Thank you for liking, sharing and subscribing.\"},{\"key\":\"[text8]\",\"label\":\"Left nav item 1 (profile name)\",\"value\":\"Ali Shahid\"},{\"key\":\"[text9]\",\"label\":\"Left nav item 2\",\"value\":\"Home\"}